  "title": "Pest Control Technician #80835",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Pest Control Service</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Pest Control Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Pandan Loop</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Monday – Friday (9am – 6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver effective and professional integrated pest management services to customers.</li><li>Carry out pest control treatments at clients’ premises in timely manner.</li><li>Conduct regular inspections at client sites to identify pest activity and potential risks.</li><li>Complete and submit service reports accurately and after each visit.</li><li>Respond to customers’ enquiries and provide advice on pest related matters.</li><li>Take care of company vehicles, tools and equipment, ensuring they are well maintained and in proper working condition.</li><li>Support trials of new products and solutions and share feedback on their performance.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 1-year of related experience.</li><li>NEA Pest Control Worker/ Technician License is an advantage.</li><li>Possess a valid Singapore Class 3 driving license.</li><li>Able to work well in a team with a positive attitude.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80835 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
